<HEADLINE>
IN JAPAN, ALIBIS ARE AN INDUSTRY 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating)  (The Week in Review)  
 (bl)  
 By NICHOLAS D. KRISTOF   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
