r k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-COMMENTARY-BJT13-COX     07-12 0393
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-COMMENTARY-BJT13-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    COX NEWS SERVICE COMMENTARY BUDGET
 &HT;    c. 1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   These columns for release Tuesday, July 13, 1999 are moving
today to clients of the New York Times News Service.
</P>
<P>
