<P>
   C O M M E N T A R Y &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
<P>
   WRIGHT-COLUMN &QL;
</P>
<P>
   UNDATED _ My nominee for Patriot of the Year is Doris Haddock,
known affectionately to 11 great grandchildren as ``Granny D.'' She
is walking across America, from Los Angeles to the nation's
capital, in an effort to awaken Americans to the insidious dangers
of big campaign contributions which, she is convinced, are
corrupting our electoral system and threaten to destroy the very
soul of our democracy. By JIM WRIGHT. Story will move in ``k''
