<HEADLINE>
SEPARATING THE UNSOLVABLE AND THE MERELY DIFFICULT 
</HEADLINE>
   (The Science Times)  
(lh) 
 By GEORGE JOHNSON   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service   
