<DATE_TIME> 1999-07-12 22:13 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7512 &Cx1f; taf-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SOC-WCUP-ART-NYT &LR;      07-12 0778
